adviseScripts.text: Commander,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: have you ever heard of Combat Ace?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Combat Ace?
I-I was just wondering if you knew...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony hides two gamepads behind her back.
Hey, are you still there?
It's a flight shooting game, right?
Any Commander worth their salt ought to know Combat Ace's lines.
... T-that's cool.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's right!
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I thought you would know.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's good.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Then...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: If it's okay with you, would you mind playing a game with me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I have fun playing Combat Ace with Trony.
Huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: *Pitter-patter*
It's raining...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Do you like days like this, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: No, I prefer sunny days.
Yeah, I do.
I see.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's just so you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: R-really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Note to self: Commander likes rainy days too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: like rainy days like today...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: because only when it rains does Elegg not want to go out and play.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony and I lock ourselves in the room and watch the rain.
Hey, Commander...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: What's your dream?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: W-was that too personal?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: You can just pretend you didn't hear that...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Enjoying peaceful days like this.
Reclaim the surface.
Peaceful days...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Are we having a peaceful day...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I'm not too sure...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I see.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's a great dream.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yes, I hope it'll come true.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I'll also do my best to help.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I have a serious counseling session with Trony.
Commander,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Elegg said I drink too much energy drink...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: and confiscated all of it...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Ugh... Isn't that too much...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: How about hiding it secretly from now on?
How about setting a daily limit?
I think that's a great idea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Well, then...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Can I hide them here?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: But...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: There's nothing in this world
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: that's as perfect,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: perfect,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: and perfect as an energy drink...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Don't you agree, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I have a discussion about energy drinks with Trony.
Trony glances at me silently.
Trony, what's going on?
Commander... thank you for talking to me first...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: What's wrong?
I've been thinking about what to talk about during the counseling sessions since last week...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: In the end, I can't think of anything,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: so I've been waiting for you to talk to me first...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I ask Trony various questions.
Commander...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Do you think...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: our squad name sounds weird?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Electric Shock sounds cool.
I think it's a bit rough around the edges...
That's right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Our squad name sounds exciting and cool.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Electric Shock.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I've no idea who came up with it,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: but I think it's fab. Hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: ... I'm sure others would think the same too.
Thank goodness.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I was worried that you might think it's strange.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony and I converse about squad names.
Commander, I have a question for you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: You have to think carefully before you answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Is walking considered an exercise?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Of course not.
Of course it is.
*Gasp*
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Commander,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I never thought I'd hear you say something like that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yes!
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: You can get enough exercise in a day just by walking.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Hehe. I have to tell Elegg.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I notice the mobile table Trony is riding on.
Just when I want to ask if she doesn't usually walk much, I swallow my words.
I have a discussion with Trony about the unnecessary nature of exercise.
Commander, I want to ask you something.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: What do you think of Elegg?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: She is competent and takes good care of those around her.
She loves BOOM and is cheerful.
That's right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Elegg does take good care of those around her
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: and does all that is required of her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, I'm glad that Elegg is the leader of our squad.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: You're right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's not the only side of her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: She's also a great leader you can always count on.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I talk to Trony about Elegg.
Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony puffs up her cheeks and contemplates seriously.
Commander, do you think the noodles or soup seasoning should be added first
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: when making instant noodles?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Of course, the water should be added first.
Isn't it best to follow the instructions on the packaging?
Commander...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I didn't expect you to flee like this when things get hard...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: To add noodles or soup seasoning first,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: that's the question...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: ... What a straightforward answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I've been thinking about it for a week, and thanks to you, it's been resolved...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: But don't you just eat cup noodles, Trony?
... Yeah, but I don't like spicy food.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Then why'd you spend a whole week thinking about it?
Trony and I talk about how to cook delicious instant noodles.
Commander, about the electricity at the Outpost...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Do you, um, know how it's generated?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Isn't Matis working hard, pedaling bikes to generate electricity?
Isn't it made by running a generator?
I-is that so?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: If it's Matis...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, that makes sense.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Electricity is typically generated by boiling water to turn turbines.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: This method has been used by humankind since before the Ark came along...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony begins to explain the greatness of turbines excitedly.
I have a conversation with Trony about electricity generation.
Hmm.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Hmmmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony puffs up her cheeks and contemplates seriously.
Commander, when it comes to naming game characters,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: do you tend to use the same one?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, it's too much hassle to come up with new ones.
No, I prefer giving each character a nickname that suits them.
You're right, it's too much of a hassle.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: All right, I'll just use my old nickname.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: T.Rony, it is. Hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Commander, this is a newly released game...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: W-would you like to play it together?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I-I see.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Hm... Then what should I use?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: There's this new game, and I'm trying to create a character...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yet, I've hit a snag right from the start...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I help Trony come up with a nickname for her character.
Commander, I've got this thing bothering me...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Oh, it's not about me,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: but rather a Nikke I know...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Thing is... after watching the Ark Ranger,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: she would sometimes... imitate the Ark Rangers...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: And then other Nikkes just happened to see that... Ugh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Commander... what should I do now...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Let's take this opportunity to promote the Ark Ranger.
Things will work themselves out with time.
Promote...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony, do you find the Ark Ranger embarrassing?
No, I don't.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Got it. I'll give it a try.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Is that so?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: No, it won't be long before word spreads that I'd been imitating the Ark Ranger...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Tetra will surely sue me for defamation...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Commander, it's been an honor to be with you...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Be sure to visit me often in the Rehabilitation Center...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I offer Trony words of comfort.
Do you like puzzle games, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, I like them.
No, I don't like them.
Hehe, me too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Just like when designing a circuit,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: it feels incredibly satisfying when the puzzle pieces fit perfectly together.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I definitely recommend Arkscape and Dragons and Puzzles.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Would you like to try?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I see...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: ... Y-you might change your mind once you give it a try.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Let's play a round... No, how about playing for an hour?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I play a puzzle game with Trony.
What's the surface like for you, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: A dangerous place.
A beautiful place.
So that's how you think of it...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, it's a beautiful place.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I'll never forget the first time I was on the surface.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: The sky that I saw with Elegg back then was incredibly beautiful.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's why I'm fighting to reclaim that spectacle.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I can discern Trony's determination from her words.
Who's your favorite Ark Ranger, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Passionate Red Ranger.
Romantic Black Ranger.
Note to self: Commander's pick is the Red Ranger.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Elegg said she loves the yellow one the most
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: because the color resembles Electric Shock.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Y-yes, it's only natural for romantics to pick black.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: That's why I like the black one the most.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Oh! I've got loads of Black Ranger merch in my room...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: F-feel free to come over and check them out, hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: A smile spreads across Trony's lips as she talks about Ark Ranger.
Sure enough, you can't go wrong with Ark Ranger.
I'm told that I have to clean my room today...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: How do I even do that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Why don't you start by organizing the room?
Just hold the trash can and put everything you pick up inside.
B-but I've already organized everything by my standards...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: So, I know where everything is placed.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Oh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: As expected of Commander...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I'll give it a try right away!
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: By the way, who told you to clean your room?
Syuen.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I teach Trony the right way to clean up her room.
Hmm.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony puffs up her cheeks and contemplates seriously.
Commander, why do we have to write reports every day?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I'd like to know that, too.
It's what needs to be done.
No one reads it, anyway.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I don't see why I have to write it every day.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: ... But keep this from Syuen.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Commander,
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I never thought I'd hear you say something like that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I listen to Trony's complaints.
Commander, what if...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I found a bug in a game...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: that all players are using?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Should the bug be fixed?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Still, it should be fixed.
Wouldn't it be better to leave it as it is?
As expected... I suppose that's the case.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: After all, bugs are bugs...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, I guess it should be fixed.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Is that so?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: ... But what if that bug messes up other code and goes beyond control?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Wouldn't it be too late to fix it by then?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I have a serious conversation with Trony.
Hmm.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony puffs up her cheeks and contemplates seriously.
Where do you like to go to on your day off, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Arcade at the Shopping Center.
My room.
S-Shopping Center...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: E-even on your off days?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Note to self: Even Commander likes to stay in his room.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I'll have to tell Elegg that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: The reason I stay only in my room when I have the day off is
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: to become like you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Trony and I talk about our days off.
What's your favorite food, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Instant food that can be easily consumed.
Any food that's made with care.
Hehe, me too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: It can be made easily
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: and tastes delicious too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Speaking of which, can I have some cup noodles before I go?
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: Elegg will chew me out if I have them at my dorm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: B-but...
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: quick and easy meals are not bad.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I'm sure you'll change your mind after having some cup noodles.
adviseScripts.speaker: Trony

adviseScripts.text: I have some cup noodles with Trony.
